1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:02,810
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:02,810 --> 00:00:07,110
Ichiya from Blue Pegasus, together with 
the allies he gathered underneath him,

3
00:00:07,110 --> 00:00:09,130
completely wiped out Oracion Seis!

4
00:00:09,130 --> 00:00:13,820
Shaking off my honey, Erza-san's tearful 
visage, Ichiya lived up to everyone's expectations,

5
00:00:13,820 --> 00:00:16,280
and will accomplish quite a 
lot again this episode-men!

6
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:20,040
Was that what actually happened?

7
00:01:51,700 --> 00:01:57,470
Nirvana: The ultra-inversion magic 
which swaps light for darkness.

8
00:01:58,250 --> 00:02:03,710
The Nivirt: A race which 
once sealed away Nirvana.

9
00:02:04,300 --> 00:02:08,230
Caitshelter: The guild of their descendants.

10
00:02:09,100 --> 00:02:12,040
Zero: The Master of Oracion Seis,

11
00:02:12,040 --> 00:02:18,030
and right now, he is aiming Nirvana's 
cannon straight at Caitshelter!

12
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:26,500
Natsu and the gang's final battle has 
started, in order to stop Nirvana!

13
00:02:26,940 --> 00:02:32,130
The power... The power of my 
friends flows throughout my body!

14
00:02:32,570 --> 00:02:35,630
I will give you true nothingness.

15
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:38,550
Secret Dragon Slayer Art:

16
00:02:38,810 --> 00:02:41,070
Blazing Explosive Flame Edge!

17
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:46,080
I'm With You!

18
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:54,020
It's time! Everyone, I'm counting on you!

19
00:02:54,460 --> 00:02:57,250
Gate of the Golden Bull, we open thee!

20
00:02:57,250 --> 00:02:58,360
Taurus!

21
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:00,130
Alright!

22
00:03:06,100 --> 00:03:08,580
We're counting on you, Taurus!

23
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:13,500
Leave it to me, nice bodied-babes!

24
00:03:15,930 --> 00:03:20,930
Parfum of Power... Maximum Power!

25
00:03:21,550 --> 00:03:24,180
Men!

26
00:03:24,180 --> 00:03:25,230
Requip!

27
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,300
Black Wing Armor!

28
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,100
Here I go!

29
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,930
Grandine... Give me the power!

30
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:44,780
Wendy... Concentrate! You can do it!

31
00:03:48,980 --> 00:03:51,480
Before me, history ends.

32
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:54,830
The curtain shall rise on the Era of Nil.

33
00:03:57,770 --> 00:03:59,670
Genesis Zero!

34
00:04:01,860 --> 00:04:04,970
I cast open the Gate of Wraithwail!

35
00:04:11,810 --> 00:04:19,260
People of the nil, erase this person's 
existence, devour his very memory and soul!

36
00:04:26,020 --> 00:04:29,370
Begone! Begone before the name of Zero!

37
00:04:39,550 --> 00:04:43,720
Now you are also a resident 
of the land of nil.

38
00:04:44,060 --> 00:04:45,730
It is over.

39
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:53,550
What the... Damn it... I can't see anything.

40
00:04:53,550 --> 00:04:55,020
All my strength is gone...

41
00:04:56,790 --> 00:04:58,280
Damn it all...

42
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:01,050
Natsu!

43
00:05:01,420 --> 00:05:06,180
What is the matter? You'll be 
defeated from something like this?

44
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,630
Natsu!

45
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:11,910
And you call yourself the child of Igneel?

46
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:17,870
Yeah! But how am I supposed to 
bust up something that huge?

47
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:21,350
You mustn't let your feelings 
get the better of you!

48
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:25,590
You mustn't lose faith in your own power!

49
00:05:26,570 --> 00:05:28,020
Natsu!

50
00:05:28,020 --> 00:05:30,980
You are a Dragon Slayer!

51
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,390
Do not forget the pride 
that comes with that title!

52
00:05:34,380 --> 00:05:40,330
I, Igneel, am with you!

53
00:05:40,330 --> 00:05:42,180
Yeah, right!

54
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:46,520
But, I don't get it at all...

55
00:05:48,750 --> 00:05:50,710
Ice Cannon!

56
00:05:51,660 --> 00:05:53,450
Go!

57
00:05:53,450 --> 00:05:55,830
Rampage!

58
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:58,870
Sparkle to Infinity!

59
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:05,350
With this one blow, I use up 
the rest of my magic power!

60
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:12,430
Roar of the Sky Dragon!

61
00:06:16,350 --> 00:06:17,540
What the...

62
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:28,240
The golden flames...

63
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:34,030
They're burning off my magic?!

64
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:51,280
The wizards who mastered the same powers 
as dragons, in order to defeat them...

65
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:57,430
That is a true Dragon Slayer!

66
00:06:57,930 --> 00:07:00,060
Magic power, fully unleashed.

67
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:03,640
Secret Dragon Slayer Art:

68
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:05,480
Hidden Fire Form!

69
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:08,460
Blazing Phoenix Blade!

70
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:04,710
Did we do it? Everyone, at the same time?

71
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:06,510
All right!

72
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:08,290
Rampage!

73
00:08:08,290 --> 00:08:12,760
Erza-san, everyone... Good job!

74
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,940
Natsu... You did it?

75
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:24,060
Damn... That was one hard lacrima...

76
00:08:26,150 --> 00:08:29,480
That good enough for ya, Igneel?

77
00:08:33,820 --> 00:08:36,990
It's stopped! Wendy, it actually stopped!

78
00:08:36,990 --> 00:08:37,880
Yup!

79
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:41,440
Nirvana has been stopped!

80
00:09:05,090 --> 00:09:07,270
Natsu Dragneel...

81
00:09:07,950 --> 00:09:11,870
You are definitely a man 
that exceeds expectations...

82
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:17,310
I can't get up the strength...

83
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,070
Jellal?!

84
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,450
Don't let go!

85
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:26,750
Idiot! You're also in trouble, you know!

86
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,810
Isn't this kind of dangerous?

87
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:32,800
It's falling apart!

88
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,740
Guess it'd be a good idea to escape.

89
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:36,790
If you don't, you'll be crushed flat.

90
00:09:36,790 --> 00:09:38,800
Isn't there some escape route?

91
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:42,410
We can know what the people 
we've copied know...

92
00:09:42,410 --> 00:09:46,000
But we don't have an escape 
route from here in our memory.

93
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,260
I'm sure you'll be fine, though.

94
00:09:48,260 --> 00:09:49,710
Good luck!

95
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,480
Wait!

96
00:09:55,380 --> 00:09:58,650
Whoa, whoa, whoa! This ain't good at all!

97
00:10:01,770 --> 00:10:03,540
Is everyone okay?

98
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:07,750
My honey! Wait for me!

99
00:10:11,170 --> 00:10:13,170
Men!

100
00:10:15,290 --> 00:10:16,590
Wendy, this way!

101
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:26,060
Wendy, watch out!

102
00:10:26,060 --> 00:10:28,020
Rockiron Wall!

103
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,470
Jura-san!

104
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:35,520
You're safe?

105
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:38,610
Unfortunately, it took time for 
me to recover my magic power.

106
00:10:39,180 --> 00:10:41,850
But now, we must evacuate with all haste!

107
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:56,360
That was close...

108
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:02,640
Whoa, man... Is everyone safe?

109
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:04,540
Gray!

110
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:05,600
Erza!

111
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,660
And...

112
00:11:09,040 --> 00:11:13,940
Erza-san! Thank goodness you are safe!

113
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:18,010
What goes there?!

114
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:20,210
An enemy? And... Ew...

115
00:11:20,210 --> 00:11:22,410
Please calm down, you two.

116
00:11:22,730 --> 00:11:26,590
Thanks to the power of my 
parfum, my body has changed.

117
00:11:27,330 --> 00:11:31,300
But inside is the same 
me, unchanged even a bit!

118
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:32,500
*spinspinspin*

119
00:11:32,740 --> 00:11:36,630
Ichiya, at your service!

120
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,310
*sparkle*

121
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:42,350
You sure attract the weirdos.

122
00:11:42,350 --> 00:11:43,480
Yes...

123
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,950
Well, he's dependable, at least.

124
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:53,350
"I'm so dizzy!" she says...

125
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:55,030
Men?

126
00:11:55,030 --> 00:11:56,130
A new enemy?

127
00:11:56,130 --> 00:11:57,980
Wait! That's...

128
00:11:57,980 --> 00:11:59,830
...Lucy's spirit!

129
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:02,210
Thanks, Horologium!

130
00:12:02,210 --> 00:12:04,150
But, when did you...

131
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:08,400
No. I passed through the 
gate under my own will.

132
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:11,620
Loke and Virgo do that all the time.

133
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:17,100
Due to Lucy-sama's magic power being greater 
than before, it has now become possible.

134
00:12:17,100 --> 00:12:19,430
I can also cure lack of oxygen, bug bites,

135
00:12:19,430 --> 00:12:23,050
chapping of the skin, 
itchiness, and skinspots.

136
00:12:23,050 --> 00:12:24,790
Amazing! Even skinspots?

137
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:27,020
That... could be useful, yeah...

138
00:12:27,020 --> 00:12:29,680
M-My identity is flying away, again!

139
00:12:30,010 --> 00:12:32,190
Everyone! You are safe?

140
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:33,870
The he-cat, as well!

141
00:12:33,870 --> 00:12:36,230
Where's Natsu-san and Jellal?

142
00:12:37,310 --> 00:12:39,910
I do not see him. He is still inside!

143
00:12:39,910 --> 00:12:41,070
No!

144
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:42,460
Natsu!

145
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:45,800
That piece of flame!

146
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,990
Natsu-san!

147
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:52,140
Natsu... Jellal...

148
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,820
What are you doing?

149
00:12:54,190 --> 00:12:55,790
Natsu!

150
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:02,450
Love will save your friends!

151
00:13:02,450 --> 00:13:03,370
Yes...

152
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:06,950
Sheesh... Makin' us worried like that...

153
00:13:06,950 --> 00:13:08,280
Natsu-san!

154
00:13:09,510 --> 00:13:11,280
That's Hot Eye!

155
00:13:11,280 --> 00:13:13,290
Why would a member of Oracion Seis...

156
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:17,440
It's a long story. But 
don't worry, he's a friend.

157
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,790
Natsu-san!

158
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:28,730
You really... kept your promise...

159
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:36,100
Thank you for saving my guild...

160
00:13:36,100 --> 00:13:39,380
It's because we all had the power, right?

161
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,250
All of us?

162
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,510
You have the power too, Wendy.

163
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,260
Men!

164
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:46,640
Me?

165
00:13:47,740 --> 00:13:50,600
This time, give me a happy high-five!

166
00:13:51,610 --> 00:13:52,350
Sure!

167
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:17,320
Can't ask for more than everyone being safe.

168
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:19,790
Everyone, you did great!

169
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:22,600
This completes our mission.

170
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,500
Ew!

171
00:14:24,070 --> 00:14:26,480
And, who is that?

172
00:14:26,710 --> 00:14:27,800
I don't know...

173
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:30,750
Is he one of those hosts from Blue Pegasus?

174
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:33,600
I don't remember one like that...

175
00:14:34,730 --> 00:14:35,680
That's Jellal.

176
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:36,930
What?!

177
00:14:36,930 --> 00:14:38,020
<i>That's</i> him?

178
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:42,460
But that's not the Jellal we know.

179
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:45,070
It seems like he's lost his memories.

180
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:47,840
Yeah, but even so...

181
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,730
Uh...

182
00:14:48,730 --> 00:14:49,990
I'm sure it's fine.

183
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:52,970
Jellal is actually a good person!

184
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:58,630
At any rate, we must give 
him our thanks for his help.

185
00:14:58,890 --> 00:14:59,830
Erza...

186
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:02,000
No...

187
00:15:03,480 --> 00:15:06,530
You have nothing to thank me for...

188
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:10,330
What do you plan to do after this?

189
00:15:10,930 --> 00:15:12,130
After this?

190
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,440
I don't know...

191
00:15:18,060 --> 00:15:19,500
That sounds about right...

192
00:15:19,500 --> 00:15:23,620
Answers do not come so 
easily for you and me...

193
00:15:27,050 --> 00:15:28,330
I'm scared.

194
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,080
Scared?

195
00:15:31,330 --> 00:15:33,950
What if... my memories return?

196
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:38,100
Jellal...

197
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:45,130
I'm with you.

198
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:53,750
Even if we come to hate 
each other once again,

199
00:15:53,750 --> 00:15:56,040
as you are now, I cannot leave you be.

200
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:57,520
Erza...

201
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:01,000
I...

202
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,090
Oww-men!

203
00:16:04,640 --> 00:16:06,280
What's the matter, dude?

204
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:10,690
I was about to release some parfum in 
the bushes when I ran into something!

205
00:16:10,690 --> 00:16:13,110
There are some markings on the ground...

206
00:16:13,970 --> 00:16:15,060
Those are...

207
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:17,720
Runes?!

208
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:20,700
Men! My toilet...

209
00:16:20,700 --> 00:16:22,280
When did this...

210
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:24,210
What's going on?

211
00:16:24,210 --> 00:16:26,630
The same ones as Freed?

212
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:30,960
It's just as... no, even more powerful!

213
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,340
We're trapped?

214
00:16:32,340 --> 00:16:34,380
Show yourself!

215
00:16:39,010 --> 00:16:41,240
Who are they?!

216
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:43,520
It's gonna leak out!

217
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:45,980
I wish to do you no harm.

218
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:49,980
All I desire is for you to stay here, 
without moving, for a little while.

219
00:16:50,610 --> 00:16:51,980
Who are you?

220
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:57,840
I am Captain of the Reformed Magic Council's 
4th Enforcement and Detention Corps.

221
00:16:57,840 --> 00:16:59,490
My name is Lahar.

222
00:16:59,490 --> 00:17:00,350
Who?

223
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,750
Reformed Magic Council?

224
00:17:01,750 --> 00:17:03,620
They're already back in business?

225
00:17:03,860 --> 00:17:08,180
We have been reborn, to uphold 
the law and protect justice.

226
00:17:08,180 --> 00:17:11,210
We have no mercy for those that do evil acts.

227
00:17:11,210 --> 00:17:12,740
What do you mean?

228
00:17:12,740 --> 00:17:15,910
We haven't done anything bad!

229
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:17,360
R-Right, sure we didn't...

230
00:17:17,360 --> 00:17:19,680
That didn't sound very convincing...

231
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,520
I am aware.

232
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:24,780
Our purpose is to arrest Oracion Seis.

233
00:17:25,070 --> 00:17:29,160
Please hand over that person 
codenamed Hot Eye to us.

234
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:33,220
Wait a minute!

235
00:17:33,220 --> 00:17:35,080
It is okay, Jura.

236
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:36,950
Richard-dono...

237
00:17:36,950 --> 00:17:42,170
Even if my soul has been awakened to 
righteousness, that does not wipe clean my past evil ways.

238
00:17:42,450 --> 00:17:44,680
I wish to start over from the beginning.

239
00:17:45,300 --> 00:17:51,130
That way, when I finally reunite with 
my brother, I can look him eye to eye.

240
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:57,380
Then, I shall search for 
your brother in your stead.

241
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:59,410
You will?

242
00:17:59,410 --> 00:18:02,010
Please tell me your brother's name.

243
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:05,330
His name is Wally. Wally Buchanan.

244
00:18:07,130 --> 00:18:08,230
Wally?

245
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:11,150
Get it?

246
00:18:11,390 --> 00:18:12,860
Blockhead?!

247
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:16,360
He... Wally was...

248
00:18:17,280 --> 00:18:21,220
...truly an honest and kind younger brother.

249
00:18:22,150 --> 00:18:24,240
Man, this ground's hard!

250
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:26,370
Hang in there, Wally.

251
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:32,270
The ground may be hardened now, but if 
we work hard and believe in the light,

252
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:34,980
I am sure that it will soften, 
and become decent soil.

253
00:18:36,100 --> 00:18:40,010
Got it! If you're gonna 
work hard, then so am I!

254
00:18:40,790 --> 00:18:41,520
Yes.

255
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:49,690
My brother and I lost our parents very young.

256
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:55,310
But we both worked together, 
and managed to live!

257
00:18:56,090 --> 00:19:00,730
Then it happened... Right when 
we began growing vegetables.

258
00:19:02,570 --> 00:19:08,750
We worked so hard, and yet... I knew that 
this ground was too hard to grow vegetables!

259
00:19:08,750 --> 00:19:10,490
God damn it!

260
00:19:10,490 --> 00:19:11,820
Don't cry, Wally...

261
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:13,430
But...

262
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:21,560
All right! We did it, Brother!

263
00:19:21,560 --> 00:19:22,510
Yes!

264
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:28,000
Let's hurry up and eat, Brother!

265
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,000
After we give thanks to God.

266
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:33,500
This single potato

267
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:38,300
has provided to us brothers a 
great deal of hope, and light.

268
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:40,910
We give thanks.

269
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:42,460
We give thanks!

270
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:44,160
Thanks for the grub!

271
00:19:46,170 --> 00:19:47,830
Here's your share....

272
00:19:48,190 --> 00:19:52,230
My stomach isn't feeling so well, 
so I'll let you eat it, Wally.

273
00:19:53,140 --> 00:19:54,140
You sure?

274
00:19:54,620 --> 00:19:55,380
Yes.

275
00:20:02,090 --> 00:20:03,120
What is it?

276
00:20:04,010 --> 00:20:06,520
My stomach isn't feeling well myself.

277
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,820
I could never eat the whole thing!

278
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,210
Go ahead and eat half, okay?

279
00:20:12,770 --> 00:20:14,270
Wally...

280
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:23,240
I have not forgotten the taste 
of that potato, even now...

281
00:20:25,490 --> 00:20:27,650
Actually, I know that man.

282
00:20:27,650 --> 00:20:28,660
What say you?

283
00:20:29,450 --> 00:20:30,930
He is my friend.

284
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:34,120
He is now energetically traveling 
around the continent.

285
00:20:54,180 --> 00:21:01,290
Is this what they call a miracle, bestowed 
only to those who believe in the light?

286
00:21:03,340 --> 00:21:04,870
T-Thank you!

287
00:21:05,930 --> 00:21:07,570
Thank you!

288
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:11,450
Thank you...

289
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:19,500
I feel sorry for him.

290
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:20,500
Aye...

291
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:22,060
Ah, well...

292
00:21:22,060 --> 00:21:25,390
There isn't anything we can do for him.

293
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:29,640
Enough already! Just unseal the runes!

294
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:30,650
It's leaking!

295
00:21:30,650 --> 00:21:32,350
Don't!

296
00:21:32,350 --> 00:21:33,180
No.

297
00:21:33,900 --> 00:21:38,520
Our true objective is not Oracion Seis.

298
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:46,910
The one who infiltrated the Magic Council, 
destroyed it, and fired Etherion...

299
00:21:48,760 --> 00:21:52,910
There is a far greater 
evildoer among you, yes?

300
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:56,470
You, Jellal.

301
00:21:57,750 --> 00:21:58,530
Come!

302
00:21:59,380 --> 00:22:02,360
If you resist, I have orders 
to use lethal force!

303
00:22:03,840 --> 00:22:04,960
But that's...

304
00:22:04,960 --> 00:22:06,130
Hold it a second!

305
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:08,470
That man is dangerous.

306
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:12,380
We cannot allow him loose in the world again.

307
00:22:13,140 --> 00:22:14,280
Never again.

308
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:57,890
We got Oracion Seis,

309
00:23:57,890 --> 00:23:59,840
so we can finally get back to the Guild!

310
00:23:59,840 --> 00:24:03,030
Yeah! But this time was really a pain...

311
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:05,440
Each and every one of 'em 
was super powerful...

312
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:08,220
We were in a lot of dangerous 
situations, right?

313
00:24:08,220 --> 00:24:09,180
No kidding.

314
00:24:09,180 --> 00:24:13,470
If we hadn't all joined forces, 
we probably wouldn't have won!

315
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:16,820
Next time: The Guild for Only One.

316
00:24:16,820 --> 00:24:19,510
All right! Let's do our usual 
banquet after a battle!

317
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:21,630
I'm fired up! Hoo-ha, hoo-ha!

318
00:24:21,630 --> 00:24:22,410
Hoo-ha, hoo-ha!

319
00:24:22,640 --> 00:24:23,730
Hoo-ha, hoo-ha!

320
00:24:23,730 --> 00:24:25,960


